      "value": "Needs assessment and baseline survey\r\n\r\nDevelopment of implementation guidelines /manuals/materials\r\n\r\nDesigning curricula for  Regional and National Training of Trainers (ToTs)\r\n\r\nRegional and national ToTs conducted\r\n\r\nTraining of Beneficiaries conducted\r\n\r\nReport preparation for all trainings conducted\r\n\r\nProvision of material Inputs\r\n\r\nEstablishment/Revitalization of integrated school and home gardens\r\n\r\nRegular Technical backstopping\r\n\r\nTraining curriculum development on integrating nutrition in school curriculum and home gardens (i.e nutrition sensitive home gardens)\r\n\r\nDevelopment of relevant training materials\r\n\r\nConduct regional Training of Trainers on integrating nutrition in school curricula and in home gardens\r\n\r\nConduct national ToTs and write shops\r\n\r\nConduct training of teachers for using materials on integrating nutrition in school curricula and in home gardens\r\n\r\nDevelopment of a National Implementation Strategy and Scale Up Plan"
